{"tid":130528,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]旅遊巴硬撼貨車　釀1死逾30傷","createTime":"2017-02-22T12:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T12:49:08.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2baf11075e43f300f7a4490d3a151c4bab38cf7","tid":130528,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170222/bkncn-20170222034425153-0222_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170222%2Fbkncn-20170222034425153-0222_05011_001.html&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=30774713\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170222/bkncn-20170222034425153-0222_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170222/photo/bkncn-20170222034425153-0222_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170222%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170222034425153-0222_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=5ef336bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n渝萬高速（重慶至萬州）近重慶市墊江收費站附近，昨日下午2時16分發生致命車禍。一輛從重慶奉節縣開往重慶主城區的旅遊巴，追撞一輛運廢品的貨車車尾，釀成1死30多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，肇事旅遊巴車頭嚴重損毀，多人被困，司機位置旁邊1人死亡。消防和高速部門迅速趕往現場救援，經初步統計，車禍另有30多人受傷，傷者全部被送往醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，事發時路面比較濕滑，旅遊巴損毀嚴重顯示其車速頗高。至於旅遊巴為何高速撞向貨車車尾，事故原因仍有待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}